snippet.title: Journey To Silius, Stage 1 No-Hit(nearly)
snippet.description:
...Yes, I can actually play and record games other than from the Commodore. Thusly, here is my first NEARLY hitless video, for the game Journey To Silius. I took one hit...But since the only emulator I have for the NES that does AVI recording crashes right after I save the file, I decided to just put off trying for a later date and present this version for now.
So enjoy the romp(and the music)! See you next time!
